docs {
  ## Create Unit Comment
  สร้างความคิดเห็นใหม่สำหรับหน่วยนับ

  Posts a new comment on a unit.

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "unit_id": "{{test_id}}",
    "message": ""
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 201,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}
